0.0.3
=====
20,000 chumps under the sea

(added) chump doc command
    * 'chump doc <package>' to open a documentation web page for <package> (if it exists)
(fixed) shorter connection timeout when downloading manifest
    * chump attempts to update the package manifest on startup. previously this would
      use the default 300s connction timeout meaning that if connection to the
      ccrma server was slow/flaky chump would stall. This timeout has been lowered to
      three seconds.

